metadata.name: Fragile Souls #77
metadata.description: Fragile souls is a collection of 100 AI Generated portraits by Wout. The portraits have a directness about them, yet are underpinned with a tangible fragility. There is immense beauty into utter despair. Each portrait has a delicate and melancholic expression, sometimes enhanced by deforming body parts. With this expressive serie, Wout wants to capture a vast range of emotions and provoke a strong reaction from the viewer. The portraits are at once striking, intriguing and oddly attractive. All artworks are unedited and thereby contributing to the raw expressive atmosphere.
